[[File:Strawberry_tree_berry.jpg|thumb]]

草莓樹的高度在{{convert|5|-|10|m}}之間，最高可達{{convert|15|m}}。每十二個月結紅色漿果，種子由吃漿果的鳥類傳播<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Molina|first1=M.|last2=Pardo-De-Santayana|first2=M.|last3=Aceituno|first3=L.|last4=Morales|first4=R.|last5=Tardio|first5=J.|title=Fruit production of strawberry tree (Arbutus unedo L.) in two Spanish forests|journal=Forestry|date=1 October 2011|volume=84|issue=4|pages=419–429|doi=10.1093/forestry/cpr031|url=https://academic.oup.com/forestry/article/84/4/419/664836/Fruit-production-of-strawberry-tree-Arbutus-unedo|language=en|issn=0015-752X|quote=Many frugivorous birds and several mammals feed on its fleshy fruits|access-date=2019-01-17|archive-date=2017-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007133342/https://academic.oup.com/forestry/article/84/4/419/664836/Fruit-production-of-strawberry-tree-Arbutus-unedo|dead-url=no}}</ref>。果實表皮粗糙，可以食用，但口感並不好。其[[種加詞|種加詞]]“unedo”來自古羅馬作家[[老普林尼|老普林尼]]所說的“unum edo”，意思是“我吃過一個”但由於味道不好而再沒有吃第二個。 <ref>''Natural History'' 15.28.99</ref>

